.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH wsp-config 1  "config " 
.SH NAME
config \- Manage wsp settings
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBconfig\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage wsp settings
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
config\-ls(1)
List all config values [read\-only]
.TP
config\-get(1)
Get a config value [read\-only]
.TP
config\-set(1)
Set a config value
.TP
config\-unset(1)
Unset a config value
.TP
config\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
